# Water Quality & BPA Prediction

An IoT-enabled system for real-time monitoring and analysis of water quality parameters, enhanced with Bisphenol A (BPA) contamination assessment. By integrating multiple sensors (pH, TDS, turbidity, etc.), microcontrollers, and a cloud-based platform, this project delivers accurate, real-time insights into water quality and potential BPA risks. :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}

